  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">UNESCO-Juventus F.C. International Research and Awareness Raising on Discrimination Connected to Sport Events</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sport is an essential form of human expression, which can enhance human dignity and strengthen societies as a whole. While it is one of the most powerful vectors of ideals such as fair play and respect, sport is also the mirror of societal problems. Around the world, important groups of society, and especially young people, are exposed to marginalization, discrimination, etc. The project aims at analyzing and addressing this threat through an international, science-based and pragmatic approach. It also aims to equip athletes and their supporters with some useful tools to address these phenomena. The project will focus on the prevention of discrimination connected to sport.</narrative>
  </description>
